TMq4QmHFNfFLfg7RhgFMrWNya%2bGICDiet2t7d3918JUYICAvxiAOr5FVOWTi1%2bCbXZMe7G/ebvrQSM8tQAUViZNg3g96NHnzHgcS1iQa3iKoUez3rdwG41oDKBszOZmxWlrWTUy5/IqxQEisRodaSgmkqvFkGyb1F8qQaI7l/UAHfCuCS9SANyMk7xp9SIQZ%2blsqw1yzTgg8e/MRE0DVgt7cKi40xnsAC5OL%2bgeHh0HMI7Zk/NAGBANxrAhZQhMaPT6VnmddkZDunHpouOABCYA4KsE6QyAGoNGI882vB/8SUaoM3SvzQNuNWF8FhagRjkTY7xfF4DluUCaeIzvhj9TpvsU6nVQDY%2b7n10qwGkvCaUmLgSEABSX9FddBMrMp7jQlzvpyWw4UVKFx6dDtKMnNdane%2bqUd0udUGScOq40pX49JgTCO6C8qISUNNJtT85Hg8H3h%2bYhDyfMRk518lOfPf1/WHXwdp/E3H7deT9N5D130RydYeC9SNouPGzf76Fzc7V/M4Y4M53J4JD3rF73T4GUnCyQTTvMKM6sk5FUFda3dRGR5bo2qoSkK50e0c28HTQieLEzImUNxzgqtW1M/t0ztOLUMxMV7yx2r/jgECNoxATsmPk%2bbe%2bBMds9udYDl7BuPk1JBdfR3j%2bDUyeNIDiBzb%2bP1/9Kva5/n1aAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC' /%3e%3c/svg%3e\" width=\"788\" alt=\"The bloat\" data-srcset=\"/assets/static/bloat.368578f.2f17eba54c6a0f6e3bad2fe555580727.png 480w, /assets/static/bloat.1350a52.2f17eba54c6a0f6e3bad2fe555580727.png 788w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 788px) 100vw, 788px\" data-src=\"/assets/static/bloat.1350a52.2f17eba54c6a0f6e3bad2fe555580727.png\"><noscript><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loaded\" src=\"/assets/static/bloat.1350a52.2f17eba54c6a0f6e3bad2fe555580727.png\" width=\"788\" alt=\"The bloat\"></noscript></a>\n                <h4 class=\"image__title\"><em>The bloat</em></h4>\n            </div></p>\n<p>The resulting bundle I was getting would grow with each note added, and I wouldn't understand why exactly due to my convoluted <strong>Nuxt/Webpack</strong> setup. It's just unacceptable that no matter what page I open, it'd have <strong><em>four-five full copies</em></strong> of each note. So if you were to open this note on a previous version of my website, you'd get:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pre-rendered note as part of it's <strong>HTML</strong></li>\n<li>Original <strong>Markdown</strong> contents</li>\n<li><strong>Markdown</strong> transformed to <strong>HTML</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Vue template</strong> based on all of this</li>\n<li><strong>Vue template renderer</strong> based on all of this, because I wanted to make <strong>Vue</strong> components work in my <strong>Markdown</strong> files.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div class=\"image\">\n                <a href=\"/assets/static/bloat2.df939b3.eb5fde4b4f1715e222af78e74f40c566.png\" title=\"The bloat 2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 656 183' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-8c1c94ef564d44095ab6a5a165724c97'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-8c1c94ef564d44095ab6a5a165724c97)' width='656' height='183' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAASCAYAAADrL9giAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAJMElEQVRYw%2bVYWW9V1xX2j8hDhrZJScqgqC0kNAHMmBDGQAljAknVQWp5SfJYqVIJacHYOA7BTGYwM22VSH2o1CYBzNhiG0MAz9jGvvad7xnvPeeeO/vrt/axjU2lPhGpUq9Y3mutvfY%2ba9x7bcpyuTzGQ2kYKPFPsVhCvlBEoVBQuEBB0cUxOp8voFAcpYtjMrI%%2b5g7u3r1HuhlNLbfR1d2Dlps30XDlOv55oxlXOaboiJ6ePu7RhcbmW2hqbkFTYyOimon/hd/wf5krk%2bliPouUbSKXSTMLPBRIF3MZZD1mgOcoXjGfQybtKJms56LAeZQKGC4y5QssowLTKpeF5zqsZ6Yd5zNpV31%2bwCzizG0Px5rSONqcxqEbaRz4Vxonbno4cctTdB3heIuHusY0Djf6dD3njzRNHGWNrK1v9hRdzzWC13H%2buNAcj5E%2bwj3O8pv5As0fLir98lnRuah0F5uELktmh2Gki7gfiCIQMdDaG0JXII6heBJ3e8L4pnsQHf1R9AQN3OkKoDsQw832ftzrjUB3i%2biPpdA1EEPPkIZ7PUG0dg8gqDloJd7S2ouk4%2bH07Qxe2Wdg5h4dL%2b/V8VyFhmd3JjC7Vscr%2bw1M3qVhSpWG8oMGfvQpZT7T8YNKDTNrfflZBwy8WK1hOvmzaw1Mpew8rpM9Z3PuJ%2bRPIu9V8qZ/ouHFGl3x5u7X0RPPIGE5GIjoaLsfQFh3cae9V%2bEdfbwFplQmMKMmgZl7DfywxsBLnxmYxQ/P3m9i8WELS45aWHjIwtyDJuYdtPAqP7qwzsSSIybKKbPsKMcDJuZz/pVafw/Za9Y%2b2ctUxpRTsZf2%2bIZNq/KNFSPESIGpu33e5EqfP7XqIf3oKPLTxslPIUweJz953Ci8F9Rand/wQXhTOE6rNriPjrKyX3fjid8F8MRHGp5hJJadsLCs3sZcenb5EQubv0hiUZ2FWYdo9HELi47ZygErTibpJAu/lPnDJl6js1actvECP/bUDh0z6Mh55C06aqOc828cMzGH0Sz7IEKIouzDERD8/XE8wd%2bPTqQ/iE4E4X34C